<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy policy for PageSpeedLab.io" pathname="/privacy/">
  <section class="hero policy-hero"><p class="meta">Privacy Policy</p><h1>Privacy policy for PageSpeedLab.io</h1></section>
  <article class="policy-card prose">
<h2>Hosting and logs</h2>
<p>PageSpeedLab.io is a static site hosted through Cloudflare Pages. Cloudflare may process connection and security logs under its own policies.</p>
<h2>Search tools</h2>
<p>Google Search Console is used for crawling and indexing diagnostics. The current source does not install visitor analytics, advertising, accounts, or forms. This policy will be updated before those tools are introduced.</p>
<h2>External links</h2>
<p>Third-party links are governed by their own privacy policies.</p>
<p>Last updated: 2026-06-11.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
